{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-markdown-remark-frontmatter-path-tsx","path":"/blog/from-hexo-to-gatsby-3/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>搭配 styled-components</h1>\n<p>由於這是我自己現在用的最習慣的樣式寫法<br>\n所以這次在開發的過程中 就直接選擇了 styled-components<br>\n這次主要會在分享之前還沒用過的 global-theme 用法<br>\n因為想要做 darkmode<br>\n就會需要用到一個可以切換的顏色對照的字典之類的參考</p>\n<p>我會使用一個 style-config.js<br>\n來設定一些可能會共用的樣式<br>\n例如各種顏色 也許字體大小/粗細 也都可以在這裡設定<br>\n然後 export 出去<br>\n在其他頁面裡可以直接抓變數顏色<br>\n以後想要改整體色系的話<br>\n就可以藉由更改 config 裡面的設定 就可以套到所有的地方<br>\n很方便～～</p>\n<p>順便也放了 之後 RWD 會使用到的 media breakpoint</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// my style-config.js</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> colors </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  white: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#fffdfa&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  darkWhite: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#fffdfa55&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  lightWhite: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#fffdfa77&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  black: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#333333&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  blue: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#60bbd0&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  deepBlue: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#011627&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  darkBlue: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#1d3f6e&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  red: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#f00037&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  green: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#4e9b47&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  grey: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#cccccc&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  darkGrey: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#9e9e9e&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  ivy: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;#ffffe0&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> size </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  mobile: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;375px&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  tablet: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;768px&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  laptop: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;1024px&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> device </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  mobile: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">`(min-width: ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">size.mobile</span><span class=\"mtk11\">})`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  tablet: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">`(min-width: ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">size.tablet</span><span class=\"mtk11\">})`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  laptop: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">`(min-width: ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">size.laptop</span><span class=\"mtk11\">})`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>在其他元件裡使用的話 就會像是這樣</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">//Component</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { colors } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;....&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> StyleLayout </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">styled.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">div</span><span class=\"mtk11\">`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">  background: ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">colors.white</span><span class=\"mtk11\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">  @media ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">device.tablet</span><span class=\"mtk11\">} {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">    background: ${</span><span class=\"mtk1\">colors.blue</span><span class=\"mtk11\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">  }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">`</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3>dark mode</h3>\n<p>來做黑暗模式<br>\n首先<br>\n我在/layouts 裡面 放了一個 theme.js 檔案\n這裡分別是 light mode 跟 dark mode 時要用到的參考顏色之類的</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// theme.js</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> lightTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  type: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;light&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  bgColor: backgrounds.bgLight,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> darkTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  type: </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;dark&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  bgColor: backgrounds.bgDark,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">};</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>然後 要在最外層包起來的地方 使用 Theme<br>\n我這邊是用在自製的 Container 裡<br>\n這個 Container 會包在所有的頁面外面 所以很適合～～</p>\n<p>ThemeProvider 是 styled-components 提供的元件\n用來切換主題用的<br>\n使用 useState 來做模式的切換<br>\n<code>{ lightTheme, darkTheme }</code> 就是在 theme.js 裡面做的設定</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">// Container.js</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> styled, { ThemeProvider } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;styled-components&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">import</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> { lightTheme, darkTheme } </span><span class=\"mtk7\">from</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;@layouts/theme&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">export</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">default</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">Container</span><span class=\"mtk1\">({ </span><span class=\"mtk19 mtki\">children</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk19 mtki\">location</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> }) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> [theme, setTheme] </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> React.</span><span class=\"mtk6\">useState</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;dark&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> isDarkTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> theme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">===</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;dark&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">const</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">toggleTheme</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> () </span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">setTheme</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(isDarkTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;light&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;dark&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk7\">return</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">ThemeProvider</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk6\">theme</span><span class=\"mtk7\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{isDarkTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">?</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> darkTheme </span><span class=\"mtk7\">:</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> lightTheme}&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">      &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;...children&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">Layout</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk15 mtki\">ThemeProvider</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  );</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>以上大致上就是這次第一次做暗黑模式的作法<br>\n我覺得還不錯～<br>\n在一個 config 裡面設定共用樣式也是很方便管理</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>額外小功能</h3>\n<p>這次的切換開關 我另外下了一點點工<br>\n覺得做出來很有趣ＸＤ</p>\n<p>是一個 白天/晚上的切換感的按鈕～<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 294px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dead7b675cfb640bc939d538384c7486/04a86/darkmode-btn.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.423312883435585%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"image\"\n        src=\"/static/dead7b675cfb640bc939d538384c7486/04a86/darkmode-btn.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dead7b675cfb640bc939d538384c7486/222b7/darkmode-btn.png 163w,\n/static/dead7b675cfb640bc939d538384c7486/04a86/darkmode-btn.png 294w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 294px) 100vw, 294px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n是顆太陽與月亮<br>\n太陽搭配雲，月亮搭配星星<br>\n本來是想用 pseudo-class 做的<br>\n但不知道為什麼 在手機版上都看不到 ＱＱ<br>\n如果有人知道怎麼回事 可以告訴我ㄇ ＸＤ</p>\n<p>總之 這個小按鈕 我很喜歡\n基本上樣式切換是用 css:checked 做出來的<br>\n外層是一個 label+input(checkbox)</p>\n<p>以上是這次的分享～～<br>\n希望有人會看到</p>\n<p>如果有什麼問題 可以在下面留言<br>\n也可以用右上角的 Contact 留訊息給我～～（如果有人在看的話ＸＤ）\n👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .abyss { background-color: #000c18; }\n  .abyss .mtki { font-style: italic; }\n  .abyss .mtk3 { color: #384887; }\n  .abyss .mtk7 { color: #225588; }\n  .abyss .mtk1 { color: #6688CC; }\n  .abyss .mtk15 { color: #9966B8; }\n  .abyss .mtk11 { color: #22AA44; }\n  .abyss .mtk6 { color: #DDBB88; }\n  .abyss .mtk19 { color: #2277FF; }\n  .abyss .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>","frontmatter":{"date":"September 15, 2022","path":"/blog/from-hexo-to-gatsby-3","title":"Gatsby用起來_黑暗模式","type":"blog","image_cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1422207049116-cfaf69531072?fit=crop&w=1000&q=80"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2d9d5868-875c-56fc-8943-3b8a65e96d7d","frontmatter__path":"/blog/from-hexo-to-gatsby-3","__params":{"frontmatter__path":"blog"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3764592887"]}